{"tid":2084581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師公會主席：條文都冇 我連想評論都無從入手！","createTime":"2020-06-29T10:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:08:07.000Z","uid":7542,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5e40067c99e48f92a30d5b5e05f9d6d987dafb","tid":2084581,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>戴啟思心諗：Am I a joke to you? </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會主席戴啓思，<strong>致函律政司司長鄭若驊和政制及内地事務局局長曾國衞</strong>，<strong>表示法律界人士有緊急需要，了解「港區國安法」的要點</strong>，希望鄭若驊能夠盡力解説。戴啓思表示，「港區國安法」似乎即將頒布，但將影響個人權利和義務的内地法律引入香港，<strong>而不經過立法會審議是憲制上的創新做法，至今很少人看過草案内容，確實是不尋常的情況</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n戴啓思表示，<strong>法律界無法循以往的正常途徑查詢律政司</strong>，例如當中的條款會否或者如何影響目前的檢控政策，如何確保《香港人權法案條例》的相關保障，以及陪審團等安排，<strong>法律界亦關注如何定義分裂、顛覆國家政權，以及勾結外部勢力等</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534726-20200629.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534726-20200629.htm&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=711a95fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534726-20200629.htm&h=fd47db21\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534726-20200629.htm</a>"},{"pid":"682b20f18394e293e2e1c5d41818f997a0c2652e","tid":2084581,"uid":7542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:15:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi7ZF_dgqG3s&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=5655e236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s</a> <br />\n<br />\n剪片時聽了超過十次，但每次都起哂雞皮，去到最後都係忍唔住喊。<br />\n<br />\n如果你開始恐懼、退縮、氣餒 &mdash; 閉起雙眼，由頭聽到尾。提醒自己，你不是孤單的；亦不要讓其他抗爭者感到孤單。"},{"pid":"be0eb2e6b5a8474c0a1477733979b89e2673aea2"