會q事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca0a4ddce0f7f3ba0b8f942ea3193a67722318e","tid":2084581,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8750a8cba5e71754113a091689ce0118d53ef477","tid":2084581,"uid":185652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:34:46.000Z","msg":"國安法案件真係打律政屍搵QC打or拎意見會唔會勾結外部勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31377ff2a2194aaf10a5d17cf9601264417634f5","tid":2084581,"uid":332804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:38:52.000Z","msg":"當你仲覺得法律係政權同人民嘅合約，條文細節好重要，中共係覺得法律只係工具，人民係我靠武力搶番黎，我想點就係點。"},{"pid":"79a5ca7a73dd0ac23ba04183ead2d26720f04bce","tid":2084581,"uid":199689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"淋病都未睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de561f2b0f6f33fe003fbd64ce795b938582366","tid":2084581,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"討論條文根本冇意義<br />\n有條文中共都唔會跟"},{"pid":"f6ebab105ee1b21fbfe38a91e140eb2bb483b80d","tid":2084581,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"睇完你地最多咪遊行反對下"},{"pid":"c7ab4bcf57faea56ead5246c0d58c50f9c4671d0","tid":2084581,"uid":103363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"見到班律師仲戇鳩鳩咁對住條濕鳩法例左屌右屌其實真係好可悲<br />\n香港嘅精英連批評都要對錯題<br />\n唔知佢地有心對錯定真心對錯啦"},{"pid":"308aef9beb5b9513da93b0db87aac2b034d4d315","tid":2084581,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:55:13.000Z","msg":"創新做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949d5fad56187cd46ab141c1ac4b6e60c3cc6b13","tid":2084581,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"this is china. jpg<br />\n<br />\n黑箱作業大國"},{"pid":"1d6395c294eedfce32207116766f854db282b6b9","tid":2084581,"uid":173179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"講真支那真係當你哋班假髮黨奇珍異獸咁撚咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080d1b1e8a70e91be61fb81a5f0dceb6dfd4aecd","tid":2084581,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"手足大家71見<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=8b9bebdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"ec0eacd28c58c204b27515081024ab23e34675d4","tid":2084581,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:11:13.000Z","msg":"就係唔想比你地屌 所以先收埋<br />\n司法制度 立法制度都淪陷左啦<br />\n不如向外國求救仲好啦"},{"pid":"1cd9c20fea6ef52e65cc5c6f77ee72d6530d9d4a","tid":2084581,"uid":147182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"法治未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2543f68ca323567ebbaa2fd99bd8d143f8c8ce11","tid":2084581,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180ffe9a6e515f4d9fffe5b76f47100556559fc2","tid":2084581,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"根本就係班法律撚仲未訓醒，人地一早架空哂你地啦，死攬住法治把撚咩<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地有得移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126b945d8768978aa386de3ce14fd19e07bee26c","tid":2084581,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"同鬼佬飲茶都可以係勾結外國勢力,危害國家安全,欲加之罪何患無詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8d6caf3078bd03c1900cea56b229a1fc252385","tid":2084581,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1de561f2b0f6f33fe003fbd64ce795b938582366","tid":2084581,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"討論條文根本冇意義<br />\n有條文中共都唔會跟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"重點"},{"pid":"cc0af133b301589ba4a89af4221fcfa447a01bf6","tid":20